videos.headline: LSU RB keeps legs moving for TD
videos.description: LSU running back Clyde Edwards-Helaire shows off the strength and drives his legs for a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: LSU WR goes up top for TD catch
videos.description: LSU Stephen Sullivan shows off the athleticism and leaps for the 38-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: LSU RB powers way into end zone
videos.description: LSU running back Nick Brossette powers through a tackle and scores the 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU TE wide open for easy TD
videos.description: LSU tight end Foster Moreau is uncovered and walks into the end zone for the 13-yard touchdown catch.
